headline.main: No. 7 Arizona Pulls Away to Beat Arizona State 73-60
headline.print_headline: No. 7 Arizona Pulls Away to Beat Arizona State 73-60

lead_paragraph: Tony Bellew caused a huge upset by stepping up two weights and stopping an incapacitated David Haye in the 11th round in a gripping, all-British heavyweight grudge fight at the O2 Arena on Saturday.
